	* src/search.c: Fixed non-regexp mode escape bug.
	* src/ure.c: Added character classes :gfx: and :drcs:.
	* src/exp-gfx.c: Fixed DRCS display.
	* src/exp-txt.c: Fixed color reset (VT100).

